# Runtime state — the server rewrites these constantly. Tracking them in git
# keeps the live server's working tree permanently "dirty", which silently
# blocks `git pull` in auto-update.ps1. Keep all of data/ out of git (back it up
# separately). This also covers per-user Brightspace credentials and browser
# profiles under data/assignments/, which must never be committed.
data/
